# Mailbox.org
IMAPAccount mailboxorg
Host imap.mailbox.org
User robin@hirobin.nl
PassCmd "gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.mailboxorgpass.gpg 2> /dev/null"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore mailboxorg-remote
Account mailboxorg

MaildirStore mailboxorg-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/mailboxorg/
Inbox ~/.mail/mailboxorg/inbox

Channel mailboxorg
Far :mailboxorg-remote:
Near :mailboxorg-local:
Patterns *
Sync All
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
